At E&T Intelligence, we redefine the boundaries of automation with our comprehensive range of AI-powered self-driving solutions with customized manipulation for heavy-duty, heavy-load operations in heavy industries and beyond. 

We specialize and are passionate about developing and deploying:  

1. Self-Driving Heavy-duty Specialized Vehicles for industrial applications;

2. Automated Haulage System (AHS) Management to optimize logistics and transport;

3. Remote-Controlled Vehicle/Robot Systems for enhanced operational flexibility;

4. Intelligent Inspection Robots that streamline maintenance processes;

5. Surveillance Robots to enhance security and monitoring capabilities.

We look forward to partnering you to transform your operations with our autonomous solutions.
